.Dd May 31, 2026
.Dt far 1
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm far
.Nd resolve Finder aliases
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm far
.Ar file
.Sh DESCRIPTION
If
.Ar file
names a Finder alias, then
.Nm
resolves it, and displays the resulting path.
.Sh EXIT STATUS
.Nm
exits 0 if it successfuly resolves
.Ar file ,
and >0 if an error occurs.
.Sh BUGS
Ideally, the exit status would distinguish between failing because
.Ar file
does not name a Finder alias, and failing because of another error.
However, this is impossible because the Core Foundation function
CFURLCreateBookmarkDataFromFile() does not make this distinction.
